            <title>[LU-8620] Get rid of mystery object &apos;???&lt;object#138&gt;&apos; from the output of zdb</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8620</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It turned out the objects are object accounting objects and somehow they are created under MASTER_NODE_OBJ. We should create them under root directory of dataset.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
